import { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom' import UserProfile from './UserProfile' const DetailScreen = () => { const params = useParams(); const [userDetails, setUserDetails] = useState({User : ''}); const findUserById = () => fetch(`https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users/${params.id}`) .then(res => res.json()) .then(user => setUserDetails(user)); useEffect(findUserById, []); console.log(userDetails); return ( <>

    Basic Information

{userDetails.id}

{userDetails.name}

{userDetails.username}

{userDetails.email}

{userDetails.phone}

{userDetails.website}

{userDetails.company.name}

{userDetails.address.street}, {userDetails.address.suite}, {userDetails.address.city}

{userDetails.address.zipcode}

) } export default DetailScreen;
